content: Hello Jeyachandran! Thanks for dropping by. I'm Jeyachandran, the hiring officer, and I'm excited to conduct this technical round of the job interview. Please feel free to take a look at your resume and be ready to answer some questions. We'll dive right into it! Can you walk me through your previous experience as a React Developer at SKEWESS TECH? What was your primary responsibility, and what were some of the notable features you developed?
